  "description": {
   "en": "By the Reiwa era, delinquents have been completely eliminated even from schools of magic...or so everyone thought. Even the \"Black Magic Dormitory\", formerly a wild and out of control place where the dark magic ne'er-do-wells gathered, is now on the verge of being demolished due to no new students having been placed into it for ages. The dorm's poor environment, residents receiving scorn and distain from teachers, and resulting low prospects of employment after graduation made the dorm's popularity sharply drop starting with Gen Z...until this year, when three female students are placed into it! So each of them makes an oath to themselves that they'll escape from the dorm, no matter what happens to the other two! \n\nHowever, those girls do not yet know the dreadful prophecy, which will affect the entire magical world, that is descending upon them.\n\n(Source: Shogakukan)",
   "ja": "ヤンキーは魔法学校でも絶滅寸前！\n\n時は令和。かつてワルが集い荒れた【黒魔法寮】も、入寮者が途絶え廃寮寸前。だが今年の入寮生はなんと女子が3人！環境劣悪、先生に忌み嫌われ、卒業後の就職率も低い。黒魔法寮の現状を見た彼女達は、それぞれ胸に誓う。ここから脱出するのだ――他の2人はどうなってもいいから！"
  },
